property.value: I love drinking at Javy's. No hipsters like at Robinson's.

property.name: message

property.name: message
property.value: I may be drinking too much, but...I think I just saw Roundier Haia climb over a wall? I don't know, it all happened pretty fast.

property.name: message
property.value: ...What are you doing here? You look too young to be at a bar.

property.name: message
property.value: I like the vibe down here at Robinson's. Not like the hipsters over at Tipson's.

property.name: message
property.value: Sitting down here by the water, drinking with friends. What could be better?

property.name: message
property.value: I think I saw Roundier Haia come through here. He looked like he was in a hurry.

property.name: message
property.value: Kanakan has the best wine, don't you think? ... wait, how old are you?

property.name: message
property.value: Have you ever seen a Sindar ruin before? I'd like to see one.

property.name: message
property.value: Sarian's technique was eons above any other fencer. He made the Falcon style his own.

property.name: message
property.value: You don't know what you're talking about! Valeria beat Sarian twice!

property.name: message
property.value: No, I'm the best fencer. I could beat all of them

property.name: message
property.value: Lucas, if you tried to hold a sword you would cut your hand off. Get real.

property.name: message
property.value: Valentina is the real deal. She'd run the table on these old fogeys.

property.name: message
property.value: Best seat in the house. Nothin like looking at some roof shingles while I drink.

property.name: message
property.value: I wish I could get a job down at the vineyard. Those people have it made.

property.name: message
property.value: Can you believe that table just yelling about fencers? I'd rather talk about something more interesting: grapes. Wouldn't everybody rather talk about grapes?

property.name: message
property.value: Have I seen Roundier Haia? Nop

property.name: message
property.value: Shouldn't you be back at home?
